  "prompt": "Where can I see a Lamborghini in Bangalore?",
  "response": "In Bangalore, you can see Lamborghinis in various places:\n\n1. **Lamborghini Dealerships**: Visit the official Lamborghini showroom in Bangalore.\n   - Lamborghini Bengaluru: Located at Vittal Mallya Road, close to UB City.\n\n2. **Supercar Events and Shows**: Bangalore often hosts automobile exhibitions and supercar events where luxury cars like Lamborghinis are displayed.\n\n3. **Luxury Hotels and Areas**: Certain luxury hotels and upscale areas in Bangalore are popular spots where car enthusiasts might see Lamborghinis parked or driven around.\n   - UB City Mall: A high-end mall where luxury cars often make appearances.\n   - Lavelle Road and Vittal Mallya Road: Upscale areas where supercars are frequently seen.\n\n4. **Automobile Clubs and Meetups**: There are various supercar clubs and enthusiasts' groups in Bangalore that organize meets and drives where owners bring their Lamborghinis.\n\n5. **Prestige Auto Works**: Sometimes high-end garages and auto repair shops servicing Lamborghinis may be an interesting place to see these cars.\n\nChecking social media pages of such events, showrooms, and clubs can keep you updated on upcoming opportunities to see Lamborghinis in Bangalore.",
